Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,志穗！中場！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,めぐみ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,必死になって...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,還有拚盡全力...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,一緒に戦っている...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,一同奮戰著的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,仲間がいるから！
