Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,渡さない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不會交給你們！
