Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,像是火上澆了石油一樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それを言うなら「油」でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是火上澆“油”才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルミナス！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Luminous！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,力を合わせるポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,將力量結合起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,漲る勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂揚之勇氣
