Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,話我就撂這了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,次は絶対に...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,下次我們絕對...
